history.content: L&S CS students have the option to choose between math 54 or EE 16B, EE 16A is still required. Since you've taken math 54 already, you just need EE 16A

Hi,

I heard that 54 is being waived for L&S CS and that 16B is allowed as a substitute class. However, if we have already taken 54, we do not need to take 16b and can get by with just taking 16a, correct? Heard this from a friend and just wanted confirmation.

Thank you!
